'''Sony Xperia XZ'''是[[索尼|索尼]]於2016年9月1日正式發表的旗艦手機，乃继[[Sony_Xperia_X_Performance|Sony Xperia X Performance]]后所发表的机型<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2017-10/28/content_33807979.htm |title=Sony puts new technologies on display - Business - Chinadaily.com.cn |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230002356/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/business/tech/2017-10/28/content_33807979.htm }}</ref>。与其一同发布的还有主打小屏幕的[[Sony_Xperia_X_Compact|Sony Xperia X Compact]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://chinaplus.cri.cn/opinion/opedblog/23/20190408/272738.html |title=Smartphone is Sony's "chicken rib” |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124235436/http://chinaplus.cri.cn/opinion/opedblog/23/20190408/272738.html }}</ref>。

XZ搭载5.2吋屏幕、[[高通|高通]][[Snapdragon|Snapdragon 820]]处理器、3GB内存，2300万24mm G鏡頭，支持IP65/68级防水，五轴EIS電子防震，配备指紋感應器和全新的三重影像传感技术。

XZ於2016年9月30日在[[臺灣|臺灣]]發售<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com//english/2017-02/28/c_136089661.htm |title=ZTE, Sony launch new devices at Mobile World Congress - Xinhua |3=English.news.cn |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230002929/http://www.xinhuanet.com//english/2017-02/28/c_136089661.htm }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.cgtn.com/news/31556a4d35677a6333566d54/share_p.html |title=Sony pins hopes on 4K video to revive smartphone sales |accessdate=2021-12-30 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230002346/https://news.cgtn.com/news/31556a4d35677a6333566d54/share_p.html }}</ref>。

